Package: rotweer
Title: Rotterdam Weather in Perspective
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Downloads KNMI daily weather data for Rotterdam (station 344) and
    produces monthly summary visualisations for temperature, rainfall, and
    sunshine, compared to a 30-year historical baseline.
Authors@R: person("mvbloois", role = "aut")
License: MIT
Depends: R (>= 4.4.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    forcats,
    janitor,
    lubridate,
    patchwork,
    readr,
    showtext,
    slider,
    stringr,
    tidyr
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    tibble
Encoding: UTF-8
